# local-only outer project-you tree at docs/membot-internal/ instead.
# Andy 2026-05-10.
docs/DEVLOG.md
docs/DEVLOG-*.md
docs/*-PRE-SCOPE.md
docs/*-PLAN.md
docs/*-SCOPE.md
docs/internal/

